channel.title: Learning how to code rsps
channel.description: Hi, I'd like to know a quick way to learn java [size=24pt]ONLY for rsps[/size]. By quick I mean something that cuts to the chase. I've looked at other peoples work and it got me thinking how did could they just put words together like that and make such a great thing. So if someone could link me a something (preferably a video) that would help me learn this magnificent language it would be greatly appreciated. Will rep+ and thank.

item.title: Learning how to code rsps

item.description:
@Host_Gushers wrote:

Watch some youtube videos, also, there are many tutorials on starting off on a rsps like this: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,342685.0.html
Also i suggest you learn to code basic java first, http://www.codecademy.com/#!/exercises/0 that is a good site.
